23.1. Reconcile the balance of the Subsidiary Ledger and the Financial Statement by identifying the cause of the difference and make necessary adjusting entries;

23.2.  Record transactions for liabilities not falling under any of the specific payable accounts in the Other Payables pursuant to the provisions of COA Circular No. 2015-009.

We recommended that the Local Chief Executive direct the concerned employees to strictly follow the guidelines prescribed by COA Circular No. 96-010 by performing the following:

The canvasser shall instruct the supplier or its representative that the quotation should not exceed the Approved Budget for the Contract (ABC) as indicated in the PR to avail the most advantageous price for the government;

26.2.State delivery terms and conditions for clarity of agreement between the parties;

