the Municipal Mayor provide explanation on the noted delays and always take appropriate action regarding the non-completion of the project within the target completion date;

the Municipal Engineer (i) ensure that all the necessary reports/documents are properly prepared; (ii) observe strict compliance with the provisions of the 2016 Revised IRR of R.A. No. 9184, specifically Annex E and COA Memorandum No. 2005-027 dated February 27, 2005 in the grant of time extension; (iii) carefully evaluate the implementation of infrastructure projects; and (iv) monitor the existence of negative slippage and other grounds for termination of contract; 

