along with the MPDC, ensure that PPAs partake the nature of investment or capital expenditures that will contribute to the attainment of socio-economic development and environmental outcomes of the Municipality;

submit written explanation/justification to prove the regularity and legality of the hauling and freight expenses incurred; and

require the Municipal Accountant to prepare adjusting accounting entries to correct the deficiencies noted in the recording of transactions.

